com.google.code.ssm.api

Annotation Type ParameterDataUpdateContent


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=PARAMETER)
public @interface ParameterDataUpdateContent
    Marks method's parameter as an update content. This annotation should be used together with one of the Update*Cache annotations.
    Author:
    Nelson Carpentier
